sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Browser (Templates)
    participant View as Django View
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open notes list
    UI->>View: GET /
    View->>DB: SELECT Notes ORDER BY id DESC
    DB-->>View: Notes
    View-->>UI: Render note_list.html
    UI-->>User: Notes displayed

    User->>UI: Click a note
    UI->>View: GET /note/<id>/
    View->>DB: SELECT Note WHERE id=<id>
    DB-->>View: Note
    View-->>UI: Render note_detail.html
    UI-->>User: Note details displayed
